2bd al-Mushtamil 'Al\u0101 Ma'\u0101n\u012b al-Tanz\u012bh Wa Haq\u0101iq al-Tawh\u012bd 'Al\u0101 Uns al-Wah\u012bd Wa Nuzhah al-Mur\u012bd by Syeikh Ahmad bin Abdul Qadir bin Umar al-Daw`an\u012b al-Hadram\u012b, third, Kanz al-Minan 'Al\u0101 Hikam Abi Madyan  by Syeikh Daud  bin Abdullah  al-Fa\u1e6d\u0101n\u012b al-J\u0101w\u012b, and fourth, al-Maw\u0101d al-Ghaythiyyah  Sharh  al-Hikam  al-Ghawthiyyah  by  Syeikh  Ahmad  bin  Mustafa  al-`Al\u0101w\u012b.  This study is based on data collected through document analysis method and analyzed using inductive, deductive and comparative method.  Researchers found that Hikam Abu Madyan\u2019s commentaries were suitable to be highlighted as the reference for scholars and the society.  These commentaries showed  that  the  scholars  were  encouraged  to  clarify  the  content  of  Hikam  Abu  Madyan  for  a better understanding.  This study is important as an introduction to Hikam Abu Madyan and its early commentarie", "downloadable_attachments": [{"id": 73920589, "asset_id": 60505148, "asset_type": "Work", "always_allow_download": false}], "ordered_authors": [{"id": 69895475, "first_name": "Amirul Hisham", "last_name": "Afandi", "domain_name": "luvlava", "page_name": "AmirulHishamAfandi", "display_name": "Amirul Hisham Afandi", "profile_url": "https://luvlava.academia.edu/AmirulHishamAfandi?f_ri=1275829", "photo": "https://0.academia-photos.com/69895475/22959591/57696482/s65_amirul_hisham.afandi.jpg"}], "research_interests": [{"id": 307587, "name": "Sufisme", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sufisme?f_ri=1275829", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1120051, "name": "Kitab Jawi", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Kitab_Jawi?f_ri=1275829", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1275829, "name": "Sheikh Daud Al-Fatani", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Documents/in/Sheikh_Daud_Al-Fatani?f_ri=1275829", "nofollow": false}, {"id": 1620149, "name": "Malay phonology and Jawi script", "url": "https://www.academia.edu/Doc